"completely opaque areas, based on a threshold you set. It only works on "
"layers which have an alpha channel. If the <guilabel>Lock alpha channel</"
"guilabel> option is checked in the <link linkend=\"gimp-layer-"
"dialog\">Layers dialog</link>, the filter will have no effect."
